## ▶️ Running the Project

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
```

### 2. Provision AWS infrastructure

```bash
cd terraform

terraform init
terraform apply
```

### 3. Start Conjur

```bash
cd ../conjur/conjur-quickstart

docker compose up -d
```

### 4. Configure the Python application

Copy:

```
app/.env.example
```

to

```
app/.env
```

and update the required values.

### 5. Run the application

```bash
cd app

pip install -r requirements.txt

python main.py
```

